Backport of upstream commit e033f243a08e3514c03e510f76658da1e0fac3bd
("fix: incomplete fix for cve (#10755)") for CVE-2026-42043.

The preceding CVE-2025-62718 patch moves axios 0.21.1 NO_PROXY matching from
lib/adapters/http.js into lib/helpers/shouldBypassProxy.js. Backport the
upstream broadened loopback predicate into that helper so the entire RFC-1122
127.0.0.0/8 IPv4 loopback subnet, IPv4-mapped IPv6 loopback variants, and
full-form ::1 zero-padded IPv6 representations are treated equivalently when
matching no_proxy entries.

